review:
Pros: great acting by the lead;
Provides lots of insight into Elton's life via flash backs to his childhood;
Really makes you sympathize with Elton. You are happy that he succeeded. He deserved his success.<br/><br/>Con:. I didn't care for the fantasy sequences. Seemed odd and didn't fit with the dramatic feel of the film. They should have left the fantasy sequences out.<br/><br/>Bottom line: I recommend it. 👍
